	   <a name=103201122025530></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f103201122025530><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=4116&mid=103201122025530>This robe is not common</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=4116&mid=103201122025530#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=165597><span id=Scholar>EternalDreamer</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>25 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Sep 14th 10:01 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.96]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just adding some extra info. This robe is NOT a common drop. Tserrina herself is extremely rare and her bat ph's are on a spawn time that lingers around one full hour. It's insane. I've been camping her with friends every night for the past week and have not seen a robe once. We've seen 2 symbols, 2 whips and a staff. So far we've only seen her once per day, and one day not at all. I've heard some rumors that she has a set spawn time, but so far I see no pattern. Three times when we killed her she was already spawned. I assume some people got her to spawn and then could not kill her so had to leave her. She spawned for us twice while we were camping her. I'm not going to give up just yet, but the spawn time is far too long to remain sane and the robe is too rare. Ah well, maybe today will be the day. :P<br><br>One other thing, if she is spawned and not being fought (or if she has charmed those who are fighting her) she can and WILL summon you from anywhere in the zone even if you don't have agro. I've seen it happen 3 times now where the people summoned couldn't have possibly played any part in the battle and were STILL summoned up to the top floor and killed by her, myself included. ;)<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sat Sep 14 09:51:26 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
